fore remain challenging, moreover considering\nthe possibility of mineral artifacts and the question of 'red edge'\nuniversality in the Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2007 17:58:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2007 20:04:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
