range of potentials\nnon-Gaussianity can be substantial, within the reach of current observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2007 20:14:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Aug 2007 21:40:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
