ce against the random hypothesis, robust TLP sites and those of lunar\noutgassing correlate strongly, further arguing for the reality of TLPs.\n[Abstract abridged.]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2007 03:20:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-06-28"}
